rows.label: qst650414_msg0001
rows.name: Oh, that child looks distraught...

rows.label: qst650414_msg0002
rows.name: Say no more, Homura! I know what to do!

rows.label: qst650414_msg0003
rows.name: Hey there... Everything okay?

rows.label: qst650414_msg0004
rows.name:
My parents have gone out
and they've been away for
a really long time...

rows.label: qst650414_msg0005
rows.name: And now you're hungry and upset?

rows.label: qst650414_msg0006
rows.name: No... That's not it at all...

rows.label: qst650414_msg0007
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Wha-?!

rows.label: qst650414_msg0008
rows.name: Ooh, plot twist...

rows.label: qst650414_msg0009
rows.name: So what's wrong, then?

rows.label: qst650414_msg0010
rows.name:
A bully... *sniffle* A
bully hid my house keys...

rows.label: qst650414_msg0011
rows.name:
And I don't know where they've gone...
And mum and dad aren't here... And
I can't get into my house...

rows.label: qst650414_msg0012
rows.name: Unacceptable...

rows.label: qst650414_msg0013
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]That's not a prank, that's abuse!

rows.label: qst650414_msg0014
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I'll go and teach that bully
about the boundaries of humor!

rows.label: qst650414_msg0015
rows.name: Hibana, wait-!

rows.label: qst650414_msg0016
rows.name: Too late. She's in the wind now...

rows.label: qst650413_msg0101
rows.name: Finally! I thought she'd never turn up.

rows.label: qst650413_msg0102
rows.name: Hibana, is everything okay?

rows.label: qst650413_msg0103
rows.name:
*huff* *puff* *huff* Sorry, it
took longer...than I thought...

rows.label: qst650413_msg0104
rows.name:
But I got the bully to spill the
beans and I got the keys back!

rows.label: qst650413_msg0105
rows.name:
Gosh! Thank you, Miss!
Thank you oh so much!

rows.label: qst650413_msg0106
rows.name: You're very welcome!

rows.label: qst650413_msg0107
rows.name:
When something rubs you
the wrong way, you really
get fired up, don't you!

rows.label: qst650413_msg0108
rows.name: Heheheh...

rows.label: qst650413_msg0109
rows.name:
I was wrong about you, Hibana.
You've got more guts than I
gave you credit for.

rows.label: qst650413_msg0110
rows.name: Oh, stop it, you'll make me blush...

rows.label: qst650413_msg0111
rows.name:
And anyway, I just did what my
hero would have done! One day,
Homura, I'll be just like you!
